\title{Lawvere-Tierney topology for closed subtopoi}
\taxon{Definition}
\import{macro}

\p{
  Let #{\mc{X}} be a topos, and #{\varphi} a subterminal object. The \em{closed subtopos} associated with #{\varphi} has the Lawvere-Tierney operator as 
  ##{ c_{\varphi} = (-) \vee \varphi : \Omega \to \Omega. }
}